 child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         true (Microsoft OneNote 2016 is installed)\nCriteria        :     true (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict ActiveX Install' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for SharePoint Designer)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_ACTIVEXINSTALL\\spdesign.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       true (One or more child tests must be true. (OR)) (negated)\nTest            :         false (Check if the SharePoint Designer 2013 key is present)\nResult Analysis :              Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Wow6432Node\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\Office15.SharePointDesigner\\'.  Existence requirement is 'at_least_one_exists' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nTest            :         false (Check if the SharePoint Designer 2013 key is present)\nResult Analysis :              Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Uninstall\\Office15.SharePointDesigner\\'.  Existence requirement is 'at_least_one_exists' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :     true (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       true (PowerPoint Viewer Install path) (negated)\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict ActiveX Install' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for PowerPoint Viewer)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_ACTIVEXINSTALL\\pptview.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :     true (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       true (Microsoft Expressions Install path) (negated)\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict ActiveX Install' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for Microsoft Expressions)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_ACTIVEXINSTALL\\exprwd.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :     true (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       true (Microsoft Exchange Install path) (negated)\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict ActiveX Install' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for Microsoft Exchange)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_ACTIVEXINSTALL\\mse7.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\n"},{"security_override_guidance":"","group_title":"SRG-APP-000112","third_party_tools":"","rule_title":"File Download Restriction must be enabled in all Office programs.","rule_id":"SV-223306r960921","weight":"10.0","stig_uuid":"B3EF3B6E-722B-1014-942B-D54B65175630","ccis":["CCI-001695"],"ia_controls":"","group_tree":{"title":"SRG-APP-000112","id":"V-223306"},"group_id":"V-223306","mitigations":"","documentable":"false","fix_text":"Set the policy value for Computer Configuration &gt;&gt; Administrative Templates &gt;&gt; Microsoft Office 2016 (Machine) &gt;&gt; Security Settings &gt;&gt; IE Security &gt;&gt; Restrict File Download to \"Enabled\" and select the check boxes for  all installed Office programs.","rule_id_src":"SV-223306r960921_rule","status":"open","group_id_src":"V-223306","check_content_ref":{"name":"oval:mil.disa.stig.office365:def:223306","href":"U_MS_Office_365_ProPlus_V3R7_STIG_SCAP_1-4_Benchmark-enhancedV9-oval.xml"},"reference_identifier":"4099","classification":"Unclassified","potential_impacts":"","severity":"medium","responsibility":"","comments":null,"rule_version":"O365-CO-000024","check_content":"Verify the policy value for Computer Configuration &gt;&gt; Administrative Templates &gt;&gt; Microsoft Office 2016 (Machine) &gt;&gt; Security Settings &gt;&gt; IE Security &gt;&gt; Restrict File Download is set to \"Enabled\" and the check box is selected for every installed Office program.\n\nUse the Windows Registry Editor to navigate to the following key:\n\nHKLM\\software\\microsoft\\internet explorer\\main\\featurecontrol\\feature_restrict_filedownload\n\nIf the value for all installed programs is REG_DWORD = 1, this is not a finding.","false_positives":"","mitigation_control":"","legacy_ids":["SV-108791","V-99687"],"uuid":"B4028096-722B-1014-815E-989BCCD2F1D4","discussion":"Disabling this setting allows websites to present file download prompts via code without the user specifically initiating the download. User preferences may also allow the download to occur without prompting or interaction with the user. Even if Internet Explorer prompts the user to accept the download, some websites abuse this functionality. Malicious websites may continually prompt users to download a file or present confusing dialog boxes to trick users into downloading or running a file. If the download occurs and it contains malicious code, the code could become active on user computers or the network.","finding_details":"Tool: cpe:/a:niwc:scc:5.14\nTime         : 2026-04-01T11:55:55\nResult: failRule Result     : Fail\nCriteria        : false (All child tests must be true. (AND))\nCriteria        :   false (All child tests must be true. (AND))\nCriteria        :     true (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict File Download' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for Access)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_FILEDOWNLOAD\\msaccess.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       true (All child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         false (MS Access is installed.)\nResult Analysis :              Existence requirement is 'at_least_one_exists' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :     false (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict File Download' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for Excel)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_FILEDOWNLOAD\\excel.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       false (All child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         true (MS Excel is installed.)\nCriteria        :     true (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict File Download' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for Groove and OneDrive)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_FILEDOWNLOAD\\groove.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       true (All child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         false (Microsoft OneDrive for Business 2016 is installed)\nResult Analysis :              Existence requirement is 'at_least_one_exists' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :     false (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest 