 (IE Security 'Restrict File Download' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for Publisher)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_FILEDOWNLOAD\\mspub.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       false (All child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         true (MS Publisher is installed.)\nCriteria        :     true (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict File Download' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for Visio)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_FILEDOWNLOAD\\visio.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       true (All child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         false (MS Visio is installed.)\nResult Analysis :              Existence requirement is 'at_least_one_exists' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :     false (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict File Download' is set to 'Enabled' and the check box is selected for Word)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\FEATURE_RESTRICT_FILEDOWNLOAD\\winword.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       false (All child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         true (MS Word is installed.)\nCriteria        :     false (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (IE Security 'Restrict File Download' is