t Analysis :              Existence requirement is 'at_least_one_exists' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :     false (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (Saved from URL is set to 'Enabled' for Outlook)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\Feature_unc_savedfilecheck\\outlook.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       false (All child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         true (MS Outlook is installed.)\nCriteria        :     false (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (Saved from URL is set to 'Enabled' for Powerpoint)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\Feature_unc_savedfilecheck\\powerpnt.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       false (All child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         true (MS PowerPoint is installed.)\nCriteria        :     true (One or more child tests must be true. (OR))\nTest            :       false (Saved from URL is set to 'Enabled' for Project)\nResult Analysis :            Registry Name Not found: 'HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\Main\\FeatureControl\\Feature_unc_savedfilecheck\\winproj.exe'.  Existence requirement is 'all_exist' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :       true (All child tests must be true. (AND)) (negated)\nTest            :         false (MS Project is installed.)\nResult Analysis :              Existence requirement is 'at_least_one_exists' and no items were collected, so result is false.\nCriteria        :     false (One or more child tests must be true.