 and saving of the file type will be blocked, and the option to edit will be enabled. \n\nIf you disable or do not configure this policy setting, the file type will not be blocked.","finding_details":"Tool: cpe:/a:niwc:scc:5.14\nTime         : 2026-04-01T11:55:55\nResult: failRule Result     : Fail\nCriteria        : false (All child tests must be true. (AND))\nCriteria        :   false (All child tests must be true. (AND))\nTest            :     false (User Configuration\\Administrative Templates\\Microsoft Word 2016\\Word Options\\Security\\Trust Center\\File Block Settings\\Word 2000 binary documents and templates)\nResult Analysis :          Registry Name Not found in user profile ntuser.dat file(s): 'Software\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Office\\16.0\\word\\security\\fileblock\\Word2000Files'.  Existence requirement is 'at_least_one_exists' and no items were collected, so result is false.\n                :          For 'MAXHEALTH\\katessem.admin':  Registry Name Not found in user profile ntuser.dat file(s): 'Software\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Office\\16.0\\word\\security\\fileblock\\Word2000Files'.  \n                :          For 'MAXHEALTH\\katessem':  Registry Name Not found in user profile ntuser.dat file(s): 'Software\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Office\\16.0\\word\\security\\fileblock\\Word2000Files'.  \n                :          For 'MHL-PW06M2V2\\Administrator':  Registry Name Not found in user profile ntuser.dat file(s): 'Software\\Policies\\Microsoft\\Office\\16.0\\word\\security\\fileblock\\Word2000Files'.  \n"},{"security_override_guidance":"","group_title":"SRG-APP-000207","third_party_tools":"","rule_title":"Open/Save of Word 2003 binary documents and templates must be blocked.","rule_id":"SV-223409r961086","weight":"10.0","stig_uuid":"B3EF3B6E-722B-1014-942B-D54B65175630","ccis":["CCI-001662"],"ia_controls":"","group_tree":{"title":"SRG-APP-000207","id":"V-223409"},"group_id":"V-223409","mitigations":"","documentable":"false","fix_text":"Set the policy value fo